---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layouts.astro';
---
<Layout title="Karthik Gokuladas Menon | People Analytics & Org Psych">
	<main class="space-y-16">
		<section class="space-y-4">
			<div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-blue-500/10 text-blue-400 text-xs font-medium border border-blue-500/20">
				Available for People Analytics & EX Roles [cite: 9, 117]
			</div>
			<h1 class="text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white leading-tight">
				Bridging Human Behavior <br/> <span class="text-blue-500">& Predictive Analytics.</span>
			</h1>
			<p class="text-xl text-slate-400 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
				MSc Organizational Psychologist specializing in **Workforce Planning** and **Data Engineering**[cite: 6, 115]. I build scalable data products using Python, SQL, and Bayesian statistics[cite: 7, 63].
			</p>
			<div class="flex gap-4 pt-4">
				<a href="https://linkedin.com" class="px-5 py-2 bg-white text-black font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-slate-200 transition">LinkedIn [cite: 3]</a>
				<a href="https://github.com" class="px-5 py-2 bg-slate-800 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg border border-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-700 transition">GitHub [cite: 4]</a>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="space-y-8">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white border-l-4 border-blue-500 pl-4">The Lab: Predictive Models</h2>
			<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
				<div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 hover:border-blue-500/50 transition group">
					<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Longitudinal Wellbeing Model</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mb-4">Predictive attrition modeling using Hierarchical Bayesian Statistics to identify retention risks.</p>
					<div class="flex gap-2">
						<span class="text-[10px] px-2 py-1 bg-slate-800 rounded text-blue-400 font-mono">Python</span>
						<span class="text-[10px] px-2 py-1 bg-slate-800 rounded text-blue-400 font-mono">Bayesian</span>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 hover:border-blue-500/50 transition">
					<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">AI HR Self-Service MVP</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mb-4">Engineered a Python-based LLM chatbot to automate common employee queries and reduce tickets[cite: 31, 89, 143].</p>
					<div class="flex gap-2">
						<span class="text-[10px] px-2 py-1 bg-slate-800 rounded text-blue-400 font-mono">LLM</span>
						<span class="text-[10px] px-2 py-1 bg-slate-800 rounded text-blue-400 font-mono">Product Mindset</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="space-y-8">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white border-l-4 border-blue-500 pl-4">Core Competencies</h2>
			<div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-y-8 gap-x-4">
				<div>
					<h4 class="text-blue-500 font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Data Stack</h4>
					<ul class="text-sm text-slate-400 space-y-1">
						<li>Python (Pandas, Scikit-learn) [cite: 40, 96]</li>
						<li>SQL (Complex Joins) [cite: 41, 97]</li>
						<li>Power BI (DAX) [cite: 44, 100]</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div>
					<h4 class="text-blue-500 font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Psychology</h4>
					<ul class="text-sm text-slate-400 space-y-1">
						<li>JD-R Model Analysis [cite: 139]</li>
						<li>Psychometrics [cite: 49, 105]</li>
						<li>Behavioral Science [cite: 116]</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div>
					<h4 class="text-blue-500 font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Governance</h4>
					<ul class="text-sm text-slate-400 space-y-1">
						<li>GDPR Standards [cite: 21, 131]</li>
						<li>EU-AI Act [cite: 51, 106]</li>
						<li>Workday HCM [cite: 46, 201]</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>
